        <!--
        Malaysian Standard Leave Types Reference:

        AL  - Annual Leave (Cuti Tahunan) - 14 days default
        MC  - Medical Leave (Cuti Sakit) - 14 days default
        HL  - Hospitalization Leave - 60 days default
        EL  - Emergency Leave (Cuti Kecemasan) - 3 days default
        ML  - Maternity Leave (Cuti Bersalin) - 98 days per Employment Act
        PL  - Paternity Leave - 7 days per Employment Act amendment
        CL  - Compassionate Leave (Cuti Ehsan) - 3 days default
        MRL - Marriage Leave (Cuti Perkahwinan) - 3 days default
        RL  - Replacement Leave (Cuti Gantian) - earned
        UL  - Unpaid Leave (Cuti Tanpa Gaji) - as needed
        SL  - Study Leave (Cuti Belajar) - 5 days default
        HJ  - Hajj Leave (Cuti Haji) - 40 days (once)
        -->

